{
  "text": "The H9 hESC, v1H9, v1H9-Oct4-GFP, v2H9-Oct4-GFP, v1H9-Sox2-GFP, and fibroblast-derived iPSCs were cultured as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ).",
